{
  "stem": "27129.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, being in the barber business, I had a chance to meet all kinds of people, businesspeople and all kinds of people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always try to learn from other people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people were always happy to tell about their successes and failures.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was listening carefully and talking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I got to know a guy that came from Israel not too long ago.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He worked at the Beth Israel Hospital on Lowell and Meade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was also talking about doing something on his own.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was sharp enough to figure out that the old age home business, like nursing homes, would be something worthwhile to look into and if it's possible to materialize.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he found out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He worked in the kitchen, where most of the expenses are in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said to feed a patient cost only $1.80 a day or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the nursing homes get paid for the patient I think about $6 or $7 a day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he figured out the nurses a little bit here and there, and there's something left for the owner too.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he was inquiring and I was inquiring, and it looks promising.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But how they get into?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, before we were thinking about this, we bought a building, him and I, on East 16 and Washington.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "An old building.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we pieced a little together, borrowed here, borrowed there for a down payment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We took a second mortgage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got into it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we already got something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There wasn't much of an income, but you had something solid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my wife--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My wife came to Denver after I was here six months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we moved into an apartment on Vrain and then on Wolf Street.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
